7 An Act relating to schools; creating the Emerson Kate
Cole Act; amending 70 O.S. 2021, Section 1-116.3,
8 which relates to school medication policies;
eliminating references to epinephrine injectors;
9 eliminating reference to certain training program;
modifying certain policy provisions regarding parent
10 permissions; requiring school to call 911 if
Epinephrine is administered to a student; mandating
11 school to notify parent if student experiences
possible allergic reaction; requiring school
12 districts to use model policies; requiring annual
training for certain teachers and school employees;
13 prescribing content and method for training; and
providing for noncodification.
