16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to be
18 codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as follows:
19 This act shall be known and may be cited as the "Emerson Kate
20 Cole Act".
21 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY 70 O.S. 2021, Section 1-116.3, is
22 amended to read as follows:
23 Section 1-116.3. A. Notwithstanding the provisions of Section
24 1-116.2 of this title, the board of education of each school
